  │  ├─ 25% submit PA immediately (integrated workflow)
  │  └─ 15% ignore (prescribe anyway, PA submitted later)
  ├─ <b>Latency:</b> <500ms (real-time hook response, no workflow delay)
  ├─ <b>ROI:</b> 60% PA avoidance → $12M/year administrative savings
  └─ <b>EHR Adoption:</b> Epic (80%), Cerner (15%), Others (5%)

